snippet.title: Catlists - Release date trailer | Releases 22nd May 2024 for Android, iOS and Windows!
snippet.description:
Catlists will launch on Android, iOS, and Windows on the 22nd May 2024. Catlists will launch on:
- Google Play Store [Android]
- Apple App Store [iOS]
- Microsoft Store [Windows]
- Steam [Windows]

Music and sound effects:
- 'Click Tick' by Malle99 (https://freesound.org/people/malle99/sounds/384187/)
- 'white noise build [174bpm] [1 bar]' by 
deadrobotmusic (https://freesound.org/people/deadrobotmusic/sounds/669965/)
- 'Vibe Ace' by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
- 'Correct' by bwg2020 (https://freesound.org/people/bwg2020/sounds/456161/)
- 'ADB Keyboard' by SieuAmThanh (https://freesound.org/people/SieuAmThanh/sounds/611754/)
- 'PencilCrossout.wav' by mmaruska (https://freesound.org/people/mmaruska/sounds/168102/)
